  "text": "Individuals are trained to contract and release their muscles, while becoming cognizant of the distinction between tension and relaxation in the body. Subsequently, they are directed to apply these techniques to imbue relaxation in daily stressful situations. [CITATION_1] tested the efficacy of RT to reduce stress for parents of children with ASD, emphasizing deep breathing and relaxation of specific muscle groups. In so doing, RT offers the potential of immediate relaxation through a delivery of in-the-moment techniques.",
